Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Ventinilla West in the Municipality of Sta. Barbara, Province of Pangasinan, to Barangay Ventinilla
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 606
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Ventinilla West in the Municipality of Sta. Barbara, Province of Pangasinan, to Barangay Ventinilla
Section 1. The name of Barangay Ventinilla West in the Municipality of Sta. Barbara, Province of Pangasinan, is changed to Barangay Ventinilla.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
